com.pkrete.xrd4j.common.member

Class ProducerMember

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pkrete.xrd4j.common.member.AbstractMember
      • com.pkrete.xrd4j.common.member.ProducerMember
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ProducerMember
extends AbstractMember
implements Serializable
    This class represent X-Road producer member that produces services to X-Road. The services are invoked by ConsumerMembers by sending ServiceRequests. This class identifies the producer member and the subsystem, service and service version that's called by the consumer member.
